casebody.data:
No. 09-10217. Ronald Wayne Johnson, Petitioner v. Texas. 560 U.S. 963, 130 S. Ct. 3422,

177 L. Ed. 2d 321,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 4751. June 14, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for a writ of certiorari to the Court of Criminal Appeals of Texas dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
